却要</span><span begin="0:37.993" end="0:38.790">分开</span></p><p begin="0:38.800" end="0:40.952" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="0:38.800" end="0:39.733">恋爱谈不</span><span begin="0:39.733" end="0:40.145">明</span><span begin="0:40.145" end="0:40.952">白</span></p><p begin="0:43.053" end="0:45.614" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="0:43.053" end="0:44.030">好烦</span> <span begin="0:44.030" end="0:44.242">接</span><span begin="0:44.242" end="0:44.880">近理想</span><span begin="0:44.880" end="0:45.614">好难</span></p><p begin="0:45.624" end="0:49.213" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="0:45.624" end="0:46.571">却又还很</span><span begin="0:46.571" end="0:47.417">不甘</span> <span begin="0:47.427" end="0:47.649">如</span><span begin="0:47.649" end="0:48.317">何拥抱</span><span begin="0:48.317" end="0:48.695">平</span><span begin="0:48.695" end="0:49.213">淡</span></p><p begin="0:49.909" end="0:52.425" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="0:49.909" end="0:50.861">如果</span> <span begin="0:50.861" end="0:51.067">最</span><span begin="0:51.067" end="0:51.688">难得到</span><span begin="0:51.688" end="0:52.104">圆</span><span begin="0:52.104" end="0:52.425">满</span></p><p begin="0:52.495" end="0:54.804" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="0:52.495" end="0:53.439">不如选择</span><span begin="0:53.439" end="0:53.833">坦</span><span begin="0:53.833" end="0:54.804">然</span></p></div><div begin="0:55.809" end="1:22.269" itunes:songPart="Chorus"><p begin="0:55.809" end="0:59.086" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:55.809" end="0:56.862">若是</span><span begin="0:56.862" end="0:58.575">月亮还没</span><span begin="0:58.575" end="0:59.086">来</span></p><p begin="0:59.337" end="1:02.676" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:59.337" end="1:01.970">路灯也可照窗</span><span begin="1:01.970" end="1:02.676">台</span></p><p begin="1:02.805" end="1:09.228" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.805" end="1:07.182">照着白色的山茶花微微</span><span begin="1:07.182" end="